                  <additions>
                  <list>
                    <item xml:id="e1">
                    <desc>
                    A number of folios are missing from the manuscript (e.g., between <locus target="#1v #2r" facs="004"/> and between <locus target="#71v #72r" facs="074"/>). Additionally, a number of Psalms are numbered incorrectly (e.g., on <locus target="#11v" facs="014"/>, Psalm 33 is numbered 43)
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e2">
                    <desc>
                    There are a number of folios with scrawls and isolated words written by an untrained hand (e.g., <locus target="#1r #8v #104v #106v" facs="003 011 107 109"/>)
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e3">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#ir(ecto)" facs="001"/>
                    The Trinitarian Formula in an untrained hand
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e4">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#iv(erso)" facs="002"> f. iv(erso), top</locus> and <locus target="#iir(ecto)" facs="002"/>
                    pen trials of the syllabary (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ፊዳል፡</foreign> ʿfidalʾ)
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e5">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#iv(erso)" facs="002"> f. iv(erso), bottom</locus>
                    pen trial on the beginning of <title type="incomplete" ref="LIT2835RepCh119"/>. Written in blue ink
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e6">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#iiv(erso)" facs="003"/>
                    blank
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e7">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#39r" facs="041"/>
                    The midpoint of the Psalms is not marked
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e8">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#108r" facs="110"> f. 108r, middle</locus>
                    erased text
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a1">
                    <desc type="ReceiptNote">
                    <locus target="#108r" facs="110"> f. 108r, bottom</locus>
                    An inventory or receipt. Written in purple ink
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e9">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#109v" facs="112"/>
                    illegible text and pen trials
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e10">
                    <desc>
                    Numbered quires: quires 3–5 and 8. Illegible quire numbers on <locus target="#64r #72r" facs="066 074"/>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e11">
                    <desc>
                      words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#1r #4r #4v #5v #6r" facs="003 006 007 008"/>, etc.);
                      lines of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#9r #14v #24r #34r #47r" facs="011 017 026 036 049"/>, etc.);
                      text has been removed (<locus target="#12r #13v #22v #27r #29r" facs="014 016 025 029"/>, etc.)
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                  </list>
